Package semsim.annotation

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Annotatable
    Interface providing methods for annotating SemSim model elements.
    ReferenceTerm
    Interface for physical model classes that are defined against controlled knowledge resource terms.
    Relation
    Interface that provides methods for getting information about relations (AKA predicates, AKA qualifiers) used in annotations.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Annotation
    A SemSim annotation provides additional information about a SemSim model or one of its elements.
    AnnotationCopier  
    AutoAnnotate  
    CurationalMetadata Deprecated
    Ontology
    Class representing identifier information about an ontology.
    ReferenceOntologyAnnotation
    A type of Annotation where the annotation value is a URI from a reference ontology or other controlled knowledge base.
    SemSimTermLibrary
    This class is the central repository for all SemSim annotations in an annotator tab.
